# File size limits

- Keep every source file under **300 lines**.
- Split files proactively once they approach **200 lines** — do not wait until the limit is hit.
- When splitting, extract focused helpers or subcomponents rather than adding inline bulk.
- Prefer one responsibility per file (e.g. map layer setup vs. map React shell).
